cs350f20project.controller.timing

Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs350f20project.controller.timing.Time
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Time>

    public class Time
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Time>, java.lang.Cloneable
    Defines a standard unit of time in the system. Resolution is limited to one millisecond (0.000 seconds). See Clock for additional conversion methods.
